channel.title: Hiscores
channel.description: My hiscores have been working forever. Out of nowhere, I can't connect to them, nor can anyone else. I checked my ipv4 address, still the same checked my port forwarding, still the same. I checked to see if MySQL and Apache were running, and they are. My server still works, but idk. Localhost works, just not using my ip. URL to hiscores: [code]http://sagescape.zapto.org/[/code]
